### 9. DATA QUALITY ASSURANCE

- Source data verification: 100% for clinical outcomes
- Double data entry for KAP surveys
- Outlier detection: Visual inspection + Shapiro-Wilk
- Audit trail: All database modifications logged with timestamp and justification

